@32   = ~So, is it easy to break your heart? (wink)~
@33   = ~I feel so much safer with you around.~
@34   = ~I like that you're both sensitive and strong.~
@35   = ~I like the kind of man you are, Eddard.~
@36   = ~What would you say to a kiss?~
